text: František Zeman (born 10 October 1950) is a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:People from Vysoké nad Jizerou
